---
title: Cheesy Cherry Tomato & Leek Gnocchi with Balsamic Salad & Toasted Almonds
description: Soft pillowy bundles of potato gnocchi, smothered in cheese and baked until deliciously golden and oozy. Now, if that hasn’t got your mouth watering, wait until you pull this dish of bubbling goodness from your oven.

*Unfortunately, this
week's celery was in
short supply, so we've
replaced it with carrot.
Don't worry, the recipe
will be just as delicious,
just be sure to follow your
recipe card!*
